"King of the Sea clad with Fury":
"Yo there geek! Did the quest at the coast go
well? Actually, I have something to discuss
with you. There exists this species known as
the Orgbran at the coast right? When I step far
away, that guy will throw big rocks at me. When
I go close, it will brandish its thick wrist...
what a pain that is...how do you geeks do it?

*Target enemy of Lv.50 and above"

"よお！　おたく、海岸のクエストは
うまくやってっか？
実は相談があるんだけどよ
海岸にオルグブランってのがいるだろ？
あいつ距離を取ると大岩なげてくるわ
近づくとあの太い腕を振り回したりで
メンドクせーよなぁ……おたくは
どんな感じでやってるよ？

※Lv.50～のエネミーが対象"
